cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with attacking machine learning models, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), cryptography and security (cs.CR), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Given that the paper proposes a novel optimization-based approach to attacking hard-label black-box models, it is most likely to be classified under cs.LG, followed by cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, and cs.DS.
